    "description": "依循星之轨迹，您将会发现在未来与过去交界之处，即为 - <i>『家』</i>。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259110/extras/dfdac7e6ae155da12864f6199b27e1d9.poster.avif?t=1678073997\" width=616 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259110/extras/dfdac7e6ae155da12864f6199b27e1d9.webm?t=1678073997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259110/extras/dfdac7e6ae155da12864f6199b27e1d9.mp4?t=1678073997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《The Star Named EOS》使用“摄影”作为主要机制的叙事解谜游戏，我们将沉浸在美丽且迷人的手绘世界里，利用相机捕捉那些点缀了我们生活，却稍纵即逝的珍贵回忆。在重现照片景色的过程中，一步步揭开一个关于亲情的谜团，从过往的记忆碎片中，找回尘封已久，关于爱的真实样貌。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259110/extras/7ee5a763473346fea625940415cc8104.poster.avif?t=1678073997\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259110/extras/7ee5a763473346fea625940415cc8104.webm?t=1678073997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259110/extras/7ee5a763473346fea625940415cc8104.mp4?t=1678073997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《The Star Named EOS》是一款将美丽的手绘美术风格与着重叙事的解谜机制融为一体的游戏，创造出令人目眩神迷且充满反思的奇幻体验。<br><br>玩家将扮演一位年轻的摄影师——Dei，踏上一场追寻着失踪母亲脚步的奇幻旅程。<br>儿时的Dei定期会收到旅行中的摄影师母亲寄来的信，信中总会附上一张美丽的旅行风景照。<br>直到某天，Dei发现照片内有些奇异之处，让他曾深信不疑的一切顿时备受挑战。<br>在他的内心深处一个疑似母亲声音的引导下，Dei最终迈出步伐，去找寻母亲一去不复返的真相...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259110/extras/d180556a1ce3cbc6b223bac6113ae4c9.poster.avif?t=1678073997\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259110/extras/d180556a1ce3cbc6b223bac6113ae4c9.webm?t=1678073997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259110/extras/d180556a1ce3cbc6b223bac6113ae4c9.mp4?t=1678073997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>深入体验这美丽的手绘世界，并且与其互动。<br></li><li>用相机捕捉游戏中的美丽画面，利用摄影创造出更丰富的沉浸感。<br></li><li>细细品味精致的手绘风格全景体验。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259110/extras/19218c187a794b348517e9f22a6dcec0.poster.avif?t=1678073997\" width=616 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259110/extras/19218c187a794b348517e9f22a6dcec0.webm?t=1678073997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259110/extras/19218c187a794b348517e9f22a6dcec0.mp4?t=1678073997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259110/extras/43c775530c1fcbcad40ce0764421c8f3.poster.avif?t=1678073997\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259110/extras/43c775530c1fcbcad40ce0764421c8f3.webm?t=1678073997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259110/extras/43c775530c1fcbcad40ce0764421c8f3.mp4?t=1678073997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>解开一连串稍具难度的谜题，这些线索将带领您更接近揭开真相的神秘面纱。<br></li><li>用尽一切方法来还原旧照片中的场景，并体悟照片中的真实意涵。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259110/extras/7dc72c550883fa07ed26a4fc8d948aa2.poster.avif?t=1678073997\" width=616 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259110/extras/7dc72c550883fa07ed26a4fc8d948aa2.webm?t=1678073997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259110/extras/7dc72c550883fa07ed26a4fc8d948aa2.mp4?t=1678073997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259110/extras/421af49719243637540eaa484eeec915.poster.avif?t=1678073997\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259110/extras/421af49719243637540eaa484eeec915.webm?t=1678073997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259110/extras/421af49719243637540eaa484eeec915.mp4?t=1678073997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>搭配完整的配音，让您更沉浸的体验这段充满爱、回忆与理解的动人故事。<br></li><li>利用遗留下来的旧照片重现过往时光，揭示遗忘以久的真相。<br></li><li>通过相机镜头来重现世界的美丽，并用照片来述说背后的故事。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259110/extras/f9ba46d4f731d0205d0e4ed0a8c6b452.poster.avif?t=1678073997\" width=616 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259110/extras/f9ba46d4f731d0205d0e4ed0a8c6b452.webm?t=1678073997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259110/extras/f9ba46d4f731d0205d0e4ed0a8c6b452.mp4?t=1678073997\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>*游戏上市后正式版本将支援简体中文。",
